name: Doom Delivery Inc.
description:
This is a game created for The GMTK Game Jam 2020! And my first ever game jam!

Theme: Out Of Control

You have to help a delivery Driver to dodge objects(as its out of control!)#

I also had 1 day to make this (due to me not being home)

Hope you enjoy!!

Remember To Vote as well (it would be a big help!)
